What are we doing?

19:05.979 --> 19:07.312
Hold on.
I'll come get you.

19:07.314 --> 19:09.114
We're getting
out of the car.
Yeah.

19:09.116 --> 19:18.057
♪♪

19:25.599 --> 19:27.265
Watch your step.

19:27.267 --> 19:29.935
What are we doing here?
Come look.

19:40.748 --> 19:46.084
I bought this from john with
the money from nana's house.

19:46.086 --> 19:48.253
Let's build a cabin
or something.

19:49.557 --> 19:51.757
I thought you brought me here
to kill me.

19:51.759 --> 19:53.759
No.
Not yet.

19:53.761 --> 19:56.895
[ laughs ]

19:56.897 --> 19:58.764
Wow.

19:58.766 --> 20:00.632
What -- what are
the boundaries?

20:00.634 --> 20:04.370
You can see the markings
on the tree over there.

20:04.372 --> 20:06.372
I'm gonna walk
the perimeter.

20:11.511 --> 20:12.378
Come with?

20:12.380 --> 20:15.447
Go ahead.
I'll catch up in a moment.

20:15.449 --> 20:17.216
All right.

